                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    <strong>Horse farm proximity</strong> creates unique considerations for Golden Hills residents, particularly during dry seasons when dust from horse arenas, pastures, and feed operations can settle on home exteriors and find its way indoors through normal ventilation. Our cleaning team understands these patterns and adjusts service schedules and techniques accordingly to manage the increased dust loads that characterize horse country living.
                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">Golden Hills Home Architecture & Specialized Care Requirements</h3>
