                    Golden Hills homes showcase <strong>impressive square footage ranging from 2,650 to over 5,700 square feet</strong>, with many featuring luxury finishes, custom architectural details, and premium materials that require specialized cleaning knowledge. Our team is trained in the proper care of these distinctive features, understanding which cleaning products and techniques are appropriate for different surfaces and finishes without causing damage or degradation over time.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
