                </p>

                <h3 style="color: #2f5047; margin: 2rem 0 1rem;">HOA Standards & Community Maintenance</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                    Golden Hills' <strong>$200 monthly HOA fees</strong> cover grounds maintenance, community pool upkeep, and common area maintenance, reflecting the community's commitment to maintaining high standards throughout the neighborhood. Our cleaning services align with these community standards, ensuring that individual homes reflect the same attention to detail and quality maintenance that characterizes the Golden Hills community as a whole.
                </p>

                <p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
